description: The move by a top dissident comes as UN officials deplore rights abuses in Belarus.
title: Belarus: Jailed protest leader Maxim Znak on hunger strike
title_page: Belarus: Jailed protest leader Maxim Znak on hunger strike - BBC News
maintext: For five Sundays running more than 100,000 protesters have filled the streets of the capital Minsk, demanding that the long-time president step down. His 9 August landslide victory has been widely condemned as rigged.
